bit_ranges.description:
Specifies the Destination block cipher of FIFO.
1'b0:AES;
1'b1:DES.

Specifies the following
2'b00:Data from independent source;
2'b01:Data from block cipher input;
2'b10:Data from block cipher output;
2'b11:Reserved.

DCF stop
Write 1 to stop DCF. Both DMA and AXI master will complete
current burst transfer and then stop. It may takes several cycles.
1: DCF Stop ;
0: no effect ;

DCF error
1: error response during DDR change frequency ;
0: no error response during DDR change frequency ;

DCF done
1: DDR change frequency completed;
0: DDR change frequency not completed;

Frame process done interrupt enable:
0: disable;
1: enable;

Frame process done interrupt
0: inactive;
1: active;

